abstract: Turkish basketball team Fenerbahce Ulker defeats Brooklyn Nets, 101-96, in preseason game; other basketball news noted.
lead_paragraph: The Nets opened their preseason with a 101-96 home loss to Fenerbahce Ulker of Turkey.
